Q. - &quot;WHAT HAS GOVERNOR MACQUARIE EVER GIVEN US ?&quot;

A. - Provision Stores; Commissariat Department; Barracks; Hospital (military); Surgeon's barracks; Quarters for Lt Governor; Hospital (general); House &amp; Office for Judge advocate, Secretary to Governor, and Chaplain; Guard Houses; Lumber yard; Dock Yard; King's Wharf; Careening Wharf; Gaol . . . . . .  etc , etc.

[with apologies to Monty Python's 'Life of Brian'.]
